        Discussion
        Antibiotic resistance among pathogenic microorganisms is
        a matter of worldwide <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">concern</ENAMEX>. Selective pressure by
        antimicrobial <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">drugs</ENAMEX> is by far the most important driving
